  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute",
    "Add the sliced kabanos sausages and cook until browned, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the kombu, rice, cumin, coriander, and salt to the saucepan",
    "Stir well and add the water",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover",
    "Simmer for 20 minutes or until the rice is cooked and the liquid is absorbed",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and stir in the chopped parsley",
